{"tid":1237892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次真係咁多年黎民主最大勝利","createTime":"2019-06-17T15:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T16:35:45.000Z","uid":228438,"like":3,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b9154af1953e3446e153de832f33f9228afbf1af","tid":1237892,"uid":228438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:57:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係打飛機階段性勝利post</span><br />\n搞到問責官員互推 講錯野<br />\n揭HA醜聞<br />\n特權法清算黑警<br />\n全民反警 早幾年重串串貢 7警打人成個警隊都好似覺得冇做錯咁 到今日變成過街老鼠<br />\n建制驚到仆街屌林鄭<br />\n多名前官員聯署反惡法<br />\n中央割席<br />\n等等等等<br />\n<br />\n對比番真普選 反國教<br />\n果期真係覺得點示威都冇政府符 <br />\n所有野照推照過<br />\n<br />\n今次真係爭番口氣<br />\n而我覺得最值得表揚既 係一班勇武義士<br />\n包括因為 14，16果班<br />\n冇佢地唔會有今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22755020dcbf88649899141487d5b9cf4008a08e","tid":1237892,"uid":5721,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:58:42.000Z","msg":"仲未嬴<br />\n要搞到佢地家破人亡先收手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69999d69612728ac34c98cbfa415214c1d6d8f81","tid":1237892,"uid":228438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22755020dcbf88649899141487d5b9cf4008a08e","tid":1237892,"uid":5721,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:58:42.000Z","msg":"仲未嬴<br />\n要搞到佢地家破人亡先收手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:59:03.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a71fd8f5d50ca3898f592a4a820a94994cd2e2","tid":1237892,"uid":114035,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:01:00.000Z","msg":"條例未撤回<br />\n義士未放番出黎<br />\n有烈士獻出左自己條命<br />\n無高官因爲今次件事問責下台<br />\n無警察比人告<br />\n你同我講勝利？"},{"pid":"6e36f203c2ca3ee3fd6dbfface01d76fbcd60f53","tid":1237892,"u